Axalta Powder Coatings Chosen to Protect Tallest Tower in Malaysia 
Axalta, in collaboration with Euro Façade, Superb Aluminium and Mulia Group, will supply Alesta® powder coatings for The Exchange 106 tower in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia. With completion scheduled for 2018, the impressive skyscraper will be the tallest building in Malaysia, transforming the city’s International Financial District. The Exchange 106 will stand 106 floors high at the southern gateway to the capital. The building is designed to be environmentally sustainable and will be certified under the Green Building Index (GBI) and the Leadership in Energy and Environmental Design (LEED).



