News Features 
















					<img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" srcset="/content/corporate/en_US/newsroom/news-releases/20170712005849/_jcr_content/contentTeaserImage.axFitIn.timeline_mobile_x1.jpg/1499871066009/20170712005849-thyssenkruppphotoFINAL.jpg" title="Axalta Supports German Student Racing Team’s World Solar Challenge Entry" alt="">
				





Jul 12, 2017
Axalta Supports German Student Racing Team’s World Solar Challenge Entry
In an official ceremony on July 5, 2017, the SolarCar Team, made up of students from Bochum University of Applied Sciences, Germany, unveiled the design of their entry for the 2017 Bridgestone World Solar Challenge - the thyssenkrupp blue.cruiser - which takes place in Australia from October 8 to 15, 2017. The solar car was painted by Axalta Coating Systems (NYSE: AXTA), a leading global supplier of liquid and powder coatings, at its Cromax Training Centre in Bonn, Germany.















					<img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" srcset="/content/corporate/en_US/newsroom/news-releases/20170626005083/_jcr_content/contentTeaserImage.axFitIn.timeline_mobile_x1.jpg/1499696713966/content+image-01.jpg" title="" alt="">
				





Jun 26, 2017
Axalta-Huajia Coats Thermos Containers with Rich Colors of Sustainable Alesta Powder Coatings
Axalta-Huajia Coatings, a joint-venture company of Axalta Coating Systems (NYSE: AXTA), a leading global supplier of liquid and powder coatings, has provided its environmentally responsible Alesta® powder coatings to Thermos, a worldwide manufacturer of insulated food and beverage containers, children’s lunch kits and other innovative consumer products. Applied to the exterior of Thermos food and beverage containers, Alesta coatings are designed to meet food safety requirements, while delivering brilliant color, high durability, and UV and chemical resistance.















					<img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" srcset="/content/corporate/en_US/newsroom/news-releases/20170626005850/_jcr_content/contentTeaserImage.axFitIn.timeline_mobile_x1.jpg/1498491582844/20170626005850-EmployeesatopeningofBsAsmanufacturingcenter.jpg" title="Axalta Coating Systems Celebrates Investment in First Manufacturing Facility in Argentina" alt="">
				





Jun 26, 2017
Axalta Coating Systems Celebrates Investment in First Manufacturing Facility in Argentina
Axalta Coating Systems (NYSE: AXTA), a leading global supplier of liquid and powder coatings, celebrated its first production and logistics center in Argentina in the municipality of Escobar (province of Buenos Aires). Axalta Chairman and CEO Charlie Shaver met with employees and toured the new facility where initial production began in January 2017 and will continue to expand to provide a full range of next-generation coatings for the automotive manufacturing, refinish, and industrial markets.




