Axalta Coating Systems - Wikipedia






















 






Axalta Coating Systems

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Axalta Coating Systems





Type

Public


Traded as



NYSE: AXTA





Industry
Coatings


